room_title: Escape room "Hospital Room 151" by Clue Quest in Oklahoma City
room_description: You get a strange call from your co-worker who was sent to the hospital hours ago. He claims that they're keeping him against his will and doing strange procedures... You decide to check up on Bob, but when you get to the hospital room, Bob is not there. A nurse traps you inside the hospital room. Follow Bobâ€™s clues to get out the door and find a way to help your friend!
